369
00:31:37,621 --> 00:31:41,181
You should be saying that you are really talented for the work to move this fast.

370
00:31:42,181 --> 00:31:45,621
On a good day like this, we have to celebrate!

371
00:31:45,941 --> 00:31:48,261
Cheers!

372
00:31:58,781 --> 00:31:59,581
Wow!

373
00:31:59,581 --> 00:32:01,301
You have finish it!

