00:32:23,541 --> 00:32:25,261
I’m drunk!

378
00:32:27,181 --> 00:32:28,261
It’s my turn!

379
00:32:37,221 --> 00:32:40,861
You evil boss, you mustache!

380
00:33:14,381 --> 00:33:15,181
Um...

381
00:33:15,581 --> 00:33:16,741
What wrong with you?

382
00:33:17,981 --> 00:33:19,181
Oh, no.

383
00:33:19,181 --> 00:33:20,861
I’ll refill it for you, boss.

384
00:33:20,861 --> 00:33:21,901
Please drink some.

